OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772554283
OL,3,CDashcam catches moment driver causes
OL,4,C'quite a mess' trying to escape police
OL,6,FWatch: The moment Dwayne McIntosh
OL,7,Fdecided to lead police on a dangerous
OL,8,Fchase through Reading.
OL,10,FA Reading driver who caused 'quite a
OL,11,Fmess' whilst trying to get away from
OL,12,Fpolice has been jailed.
OL,14,FDwayne McIntosh led officers on a
OL,15,Fchase through the town in December
OL,16,F2025, after he was stopped by an
OL,17,Fofficer in the early hours of the
OL,18,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
