PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772554283
OL,3,CDashcam catches moment driver causes
OL,4,C'quite a mess' trying to escape police
OL,6,FMcIntosh, aged 41 and of Palmer Park
OL,7,FAvenue in the town, crashed into
OL,8,Fnumerous parked cars, and can be seen
OL,9,Fon police dashcam trying to
OL,10,Fdesperately get away.
OL,12,FAfter a short pursuit he was
OL,13,Fapprehended and arrested, and later
OL,14,Fcharged with several offences.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
