PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1772554283
OL,3,CDashcam catches moment driver causes
OL,4,C'quite a mess' trying to escape police
OL,6,FAt Reading Magistrates he was
OL,7,Fsentenced to one year and four months
OL,8,Fbehind bars for dangerous driving,
OL,9,Ffailing to provide a specimen at the
OL,10,Froadside, failing to stop for police,
OL,11,Fno insurance, driving without a
OL,12,Flicence, no MOT and failing to stop
OL,13,Fafter a collision.
OL,15,FHe has also been disqualified from
OL,16,Fdriving for 42 months, and will have
OL,17,Fto take an extended retest if he wants
OL,18,Fa driving licence in the future.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
